data.description: Welcome to your Southern Oasis! Located in the King Oaks Subdivision. The beauty begins when entering the drive up to a large arch entrance made from Rattlesnake Rock. Open the front doors and step in on hardwood floors. The entry way has highlighted displays for portraits or artwork. The living room offers an abundance of natural light with oversized windows and a rock fireplace. The kitchen features high-end Viking appliances, granite counters on top of painted maple wood cabinets and a Butler's Kitchen. The master bedroom overlooks the back patio and is complimented by an enormous bathroom, that features double vanities, a large tub, walk in shower and walk in closet. This gorgeous, custom home also includes a theatre room. Outside, enjoy an elevated patio with a built in grill that overlooks the pool. Featured with a slide, rock waterfall, and hot tub. Control 4-smart home. There is so much that this home has to offer, don’t miss out on an opportunity to own a home of this caliber!
